<ul style=3D"list-style-type: square;">
<li>New or Change to existing endpoint get account rates&nbsp; (including A=
PI Specs and DTD)</li>
</ul><p>W1C APIs</p>
<ul style=3D"list-style-type: square;">
<li>New or Change to existing endpoint to get account rates&nbsp; (includin=
g API Specs and DTD)</li>
</ul><p>10x APIs</p>
<ul style=3D"list-style-type: square;">
<li>New INF API (1) with new&nbsp; endpoint to get account rates&nbsp; (inc=
luding API Specs and DTD)</li>
<li>New callout to 10x endpoint to fetch these rates</li>
</ul></td>
