<td class=3D"confluenceTd"><p><span class=3D"inline-comment-marker" data-re=
f=3D"aa92c361-e187-40ae-b0bf-5c15abbb56e1">XP APIs</span></p>
<ul>
<li><span class=3D"inline-comment-marker" data-ref=3D"aa92c361-e187-40ae-b0=
bf-5c15abbb56e1">Change to existing TXN Listing endpoint support 'filter' p=
arameters (including API Specs and DTD)</span></li>
</ul><p><span class=3D"inline-comment-marker" data-ref=3D"aa92c361-e187-40a=
e-b0bf-5c15abbb56e1">W1C APIs</span></p>
<ul>
<li><span class=3D"inline-comment-marker" data-ref=3D"aa92c361-e187-40ae-b0=
bf-5c15abbb56e1">Change to existing TXN Listing endpoint support 'filter' p=
arameters (including API Specs and DTD)</span></li>
</ul><p><span class=3D"inline-comment-marker" data-ref=3D"aa92c361-e187-40a=
e-b0bf-5c15abbb56e1">10x APIs</span></p>
<ul>
<li><span class=3D"inline-comment-marker" data-ref=3D"aa92c361-e187-40ae-b0=
